data.description: Welcome to this spacious 4-bedroom, 2-bathroom home that not only offers comfortable living but also the convenience of easy access to the interstate.  Step into the living room, where a charming fireplace provides a cozy focal point, perfect for those chilly evenings when you want to unwind and relax.  The kitchen is designed with plenty of storage space, ensuring all your cooking essentials are neatly organized and within reach.  In the master bedroom, you'll discover a convenient walk-in closet, simplifying your daily routines and keeping your belongings well-organized.  The master bathroom is a sanctuary of its own, featuring a relaxing jet tub, allowing you to soak away the stresses of the day.  Outside, you'll appreciate the spaciousness of the large backyard, providing ample room for outdoor activities, gardening, or simply enjoying the fresh air.  This property combines comfort and accessibility, making it an ideal place to call home. Don't miss the chance to make this wonderful property your own. Schedule a showing today!
